NOTES: People really liked this show and also the staff also wanted to work on it, so right when we got our sources, we started working on it.
Took about 48 hours to get this show prepared and encoded. Used FFF subs, timed and QT'd by DETOX. Hopefully, FFF will get the whole series done because
as of July 2015, they stalled the series, so we hope that they get back onto working on SAOII whenever they can.

EDIT 7/3/15: Finally got the 1080p versions of the episodes. The Anime Kushi Release Group will be taking a vacation from July 4-12.
Uploads will resume on July 13th. Uploads for Sword Art Online II (Subbed) and Steins;Gate (Subbed) will be uploaded during July 4-5.
All other uploads besides the ones listed will be uploaded when we come back from vacation.
To all in the USA, have a happy 4th of July, and have a great time with friends and family! :)
